---

## `.env.example`

```bash
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# Never commit .env to source control — it is in .gitignore.

# ── Azure OpenAI ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=
AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://<resource>.openai.azure.com/
AZURE_OPENAI_CHAT_DEPLOYMENT_NAME=

# ── Azure AI Foundry (alternative to raw Azure OpenAI — see phase-4-migrate-ops/4b-deployment/foundry_client.py)
FOUNDRY_PROJECT_ENDPOINT=https://<resource>.services.ai.azure.com
FOUNDRY_MODEL=

# ── Azure AI Search (required for RAG sample only — phase-2-rebuild/05_rag_flow.py)
AZURE_AI_SEARCH_ENDPOINT=https://<search-resource>.search.windows.net
AZURE_AI_SEARCH_INDEX_NAME=
AZURE_AI_SEARCH_API_KEY=

# ── Application Insights (required for tracing — phase-4-migrate-ops/4a-tracing/)
APPLICATIONINSIGHTS_CONNECTION_STRING=
